172
00:11:11.306 --> 00:11:17.879
♪♪

173
00:11:17.913 --> 00:11:25.220
♪♪

174
00:11:25.254 --> 00:11:26.622
[Light thunk on the door]

175
00:11:26.655 --> 00:11:31.460
♪♪

176
00:11:31.493 --> 00:11:33.228
[Door creaks]

177
00:11:33.262 --> 00:11:35.430
♪♪

178
00:11:35.464 --> 00:11:36.932
