218
00:14:08.417 --> 00:14:10.619
Jimmy. don't.

219
00:14:10.652 --> 00:14:18.652
♪♪

220
00:14:20.662 --> 00:14:28.662
♪♪

221
00:14:30.672 --> 00:14:35.811
♪♪

222
00:14:35.844 --> 00:14:38.146
